{"tid":756217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook展望差　股價跌幅擴至23%","createTime":"2018-07-26T00:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T14:43:55.000Z","uid":28765,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d6f53ff160b23d76edb05801f00664491e08fd","tid":756217,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"Facebook（fb）業績及展望同遜預期，股價跌不停，恍如拆倉，在收市後交易時段暴跌22.8%，報167.85美元，市值蒸發約1,200億美元。<br />\n<br />\nfb在美股收市後公布第二季業績，收入按年上升42%至132.3億美元，遜市場預期133.6億美元；純利51.1億美元，增加31%，每股盈利1.74美元，勝預期1.72美元。<br />\n<br />\n期內，每日活躍用戶14.7億，遜預期14.9億；每月活躍用戶22.3億，亦遜預期22.5億。每日及每月活躍用戶次季增加11%，低於首季增長率13%。<br />\n<br />\nfb今年醜聞纏身，先有Cambridge Analytica不當使用fb用戶資料，再有WhatsApp散播拐子佬謠言，導致印度一名軟件工程師無辜遭群眾打死。Pivotal Research分析師Brian Wieser認為，fb的核心平台正在走下坡。<br />\n<br />\nfb次季總開支按年急增50%至74億美元，而毛利率則由47%降至44%。公司預料下半年收入增長減慢，明年開支增速會高於收入。<br />\n<br />\nfb周三破頂，收報217.5美元，升1.3%，最高報218.62美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2123355/Facebook展望差%E3%80%80股價跌幅擴至23-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2123355%2FFacebook%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B%E5%B7%AE%25E3%2580%2580%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E8%B7%8C%E5%B9%85%E6%93%B4%E8%87%B323-&d=TbmCC7jMkKUGLVsP2qrxgxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=c5e5ee39\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2123355/Facebook展望差%E3%80%80股價跌幅擴至23-</a>"},{"pid":"a8e572d6a8c68b89518d67441a9681460564c0ec","tid":756217,"uid":53577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"重有豬西8格好快比侵侵拉"},{"pid":"9f6ffcc355e96d3c95d7f668b334b18bb6a1187d","tid":756217,"uid":37979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"入貨時機"},{"pid":"51f69dd0097a38e590127fa0456bffcd4e50ccf8","tid":756217,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"奶共丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a961a7a21f863f1e3f7c4e73b0544d80ed9388e","tid":7562